Or just const lookup tables:
static const uint32_t MDMA_BURST_SIZE[][2] = {
         {MDMA_SOURCE_BURST_SINGLE, MDMA_DEST_BURST_SINGLE},
         {MDMA_SOURCE_BURST_2BEATS, MDMA_DEST_BURST_2BEATS},
